00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:03,330
So here's a note to self:

289
00:12:03,330 --> 00:12:05,330
The cracks have started to show

290
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:08,330
in our constructed world,

291
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:10,330
and oceans will continue

292
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:12,330
to surge through the cracks,

293
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:15,330
and oil and blood,

294
00:12:15,330 --> 00:12:18,330
rivers of it.

295
00:12:18,330 --> 00:12:20,330
Crucially, we haven't been figuring out

296
00:12:20,330 --> 00:12:22,330
how to live in oneness

297
00:12:22,330 --> 00:12:25,330
with the Earth and every other living thing.

298
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:28,330
We've just been insanely trying to figure out

299
00:12:28,330 --> 00:12:31,330
how to live with each other -- billions of each other.

300
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:33,330
Only we're not living with each other;

301
00:12:33,330 --> 00:12:36,330
our crazy selves are living with each other

302
00:12:36,330 --> 00:12:38,330
and perpetuating an epidemic

303
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:41,330
of disconnection.

304
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:44,330
Let's live with each other

305
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:47,330
and take it a breath at a time.

306
00:12:47,330 --> 00:12:51,330
If we can get under that heavy self,

307
00:12:51,330 --> 00:12:53,330
light a torch of awareness,

308
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:55,330
and find our essence,

309
00:12:55,330 --> 00:12:57,330
our connection to the infinite

310
00:12:57,330 --> 00:13:00,330
and every other living thing.

311
00:13:00,330 --> 00:13:02,330
We knew it from the day we were born.

312
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:04,330
Let's not be freaked out

313
00:13:04,330 --> 00:13:07,330
by our bountiful nothingness.

314
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:09,330
It's more a reality

315
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:11,330
than the ones our selves have created.

316
00:13:11,330 --> 00:13:15,330
Imagine what kind of existence we can have

317
00:13:15,330 --> 00:13:19,330
if we honor inevitable death of self,

318
00:13:19,330 --> 00:13:23,330
appreciate the privilege of life

319
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:27,330
and marvel at what comes next.

320
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:30,330
Simple awareness is where it begins.

321
00:13:30,330 --> 00:13:32,330
Thank you for listening.

322
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:49,330
(Applause)

